{"tid":1583540,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人手置頂！天水圍手足要小心，藍屍group有傳零晨2點落西鐵站清潔！","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T00:22:06.000Z","uid":123395,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"08fdbef4700d7c8bede37a69625d83b6a61db80c","tid":1583540,"uid":123395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"無意阻止各位手足嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n但係有朋友响group send咗啲message出黎，藍屍零晨2點天水圍西鐵站清潔<br />\n<br />\n無得fact check，只求天水圍手足小心<br />\n<br />\n帶定cam，唔好好似之前荃灣第一次二陂坡恐襲咁，無人影到，比佢地走得甩<br />\n<br />\n萬事小心！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ht97BTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHt97BTO.jpg&h=908e0ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06r9QdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06r9QdP.jpg&h=c0dd6674&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUCUgTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhUCUgTR.jpg&h=bb0d4e0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a1182e047f9e0e25aa84e6ebf9074760f7fba76","tid":1583540,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"68585e83232436fe2d499792c52a144a0329bd08","tid":1583540,"uid":265221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"4190073148432d8df3563233cec6ac45d7d89309","tid":1583540,"uid":123395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"847aab5e1a735a4ce66a8ddcec27ec0863d3b97c","tid":1583540,"uid":123395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"942101902f9bd6944dd072fb9d78e5e11a30bc0e","tid":1583540,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:28:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">割蓆宣言 - 幫手翻譯, 做文宣圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kMrteqX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kMrteqX</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">[新行動]</span> [增加國際輿論] <span style=\"color: orange;\">推到林奠戴住豬嘴口罩, 頭盔對話</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582650</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">希望有人幫手</span></span>"},{"pid":"52ed020bdff1b89b64062dbb20edec0e57fc2598","tid":1583540,"uid":123395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"520b0833752311428aa6d4851a1b81d1cc0177b5","tid":1583540,"uid":250164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:50:06.000Z","m